        "timestamp": "2017-08-09 23:50:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe used to have a set of properties preset in the settings.xml files defined for each project in the ONAP Jenkins server.  However, it seems that for the new projects, the only thing defined in the project specific settings.xml files is the serverIds - no other properties..  I'll try submitting a change that sets default values for those missing properties in the pom.xml to get the build working.  If that works, then I'll do a separate changes to add them to our parent pom.xml and remove the settings from the distribution pom.xml",
        "patchset_number": 1
